# wnaspi32 targets configuration
#
# Only put an entry here if the device needs an async delay, ie
#    the dll returns SS_PENDING, waits for async_delay milliseconds, and raises the event/calls the callback
# If async_delay = 0 (default), the dll will return the real response immediately, and
#    raise an event/call the callback immediately (even before the response actually)
# (Most devices shouldn't need this if they followed Adaptec's recommendations...)
#
# Vendor, Model, async_delay (msecs)
#
# ! ADAPT the next line to your setup !
#
SEGA OA ,Saturn CartDev  ,100
